data.description: True 4 bedroom, 3.1 baths with a full size office and formal dining room.  The kitchen was remodeled in 2019 with new cabinets and granite counter tops.  This home has the perfect layout for a family or entertaining.  The master is downstairs and 3 bedrooms are upstairs.  New wrought iron railing going up the staircase.  The rooms upstairs are very large.  The backyard patio is very inviting with a partial wooden deck.  This house has a lot of potential and is ready for you to move in and call it your own.  It has a nice sized storm shelter inside the 3 car garage
